メソッドの詳細

getCreatedAt

Date getCreatedAt()
The time at which this KudoScore was calculated.

戻り値:
the createdAt

getKudoRank

int getKudoRank()
The KudoRank, which is an integer from 1 to 10.
Higher ranks are better. KudoRanks are assigned on a curve,
with a certain fraction of people receiving each KudoRank.

戻り値:
the kudoRank

getPosition

long getPosition()
An integer which orders all participants.
The person with `position` equals 1 is the highest-ranked person on Ohloh.

戻り値:
the position

getMaxPosition

long getMaxPosition()
The total number of partcipants in the most recent KudoScore calculations.
The person whose `position` equals `max_position` is the lowest-ranked
person on Ohloh.

戻り値:
the maxPosition

getPositionDelta

float getPositionDelta()
The change in this person’s position since the previous kudo score calculations.
Here, a negative number represents an improvement,
since lower positions are better.

戻り値:
the positionDelta
